{"tid":2061752,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一中國科學家在美機場被捕身份竟是解放軍少校","createTime":"2020-06-12T15:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T17:20:25.000Z","uid":28114,"like":448,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"6c176c227fe99aca7fe6fa701ba2c64ba6f91793","tid":2061752,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m.dw.com/image/45264895_303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.dw.com%2Fimage%2F45264895_303.jpg&h=48dfb30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部周四宣布，一名中國科研人員在洛杉磯離境時，因涉嫌間諜罪被捕。他在被捕後坦誠自己其實是解放軍軍官，且受到中國官方的資助。<br />\n(德國之聲中文網)根據舊金山聯邦檢察官辦公室與聯邦調查局(FBI)辦公室發表的聯合聲明，中國籍的王新6月7日準備從洛杉磯搭機前往中國天津。雖然他在2019年3月宣稱自己赴美的目的是在加州大學舊金山分校(UCSF)做科學研究，但是在海關與邊境保衛局(CBP)的盤問之下，他坦承他是中國人民解放軍的軍官，且受到中國軍事研究室的僱用。根據美國海關與邊境保衛局(CBP)所稱，王新有少校軍銜<br />\n<br />\n王新因為在申請簽證時隱瞞實情，涉嫌&ldquo;簽證欺詐&rdquo;，若被判定罪成，將面臨最高10年刑期與高達25萬元美金的罰金。<br />\n美國海關與邊境保衛局(CBP)在聲明中表示，王新承認受到上層指使，要他觀察加州大學舊金山分校實驗室的設置，並將如何復制美國經驗的關鍵資料帶回中國。<br />\n海關表示，王新早前已經透過電子郵件將資料發給同事，他在離境時也攜帶著從美國加州大學舊金山分校取得的研究，準備回國後分享給他在解放軍的同事。美國加州大學舊金山分校實驗室的研究是由是美國國家衛生研究院(NIH)以及美國健康及公共服務部(HHS)所資助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.dw.com/image/39027613_303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.dw.com%2Fimage%2F39027613_303.jpg&h=71cdd47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關表示，王新在抵達機場之前，就已經消除了所有在微信上的通聯紀錄。<br />\n六月初，美國總統特朗普宣布要禁止與中國解放軍有關的學生赴美就學，甚至撤銷與中國軍方有關的留學生簽證。對美國而言，中國是國際留學生的最大來源國，為美國經濟貢獻了近140億美元。目前有約36萬名中國人在美留學，當中有13萬人是研究生，佔所有國際研究生的36%。<br />\n張慈(法新社)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.dw.com/zh/一中国科学家在美机场被捕-身份竟是解放军少校/a-53784605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.dw.com%2Fzh%2F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%BA%E5%9C%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E5%86%9B%E5%B0%91%E6%A0%A1%2Fa-53784605&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=87333d3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.dw.com/zh/一中国科学家在美机场被捕-身份竟是解放军少校/a-53784605</a>"},{"pid":"505a659bab009b41307d476a2fc0633085c4d009","tid":2061752,"uid":28114,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:21:31.000Z","msg":"實捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf986e3863aba722549b56d54301530de92cace","tid":2061752,"uid":227271,"like":415,"dislike":1,"score":414,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"咁早就爆定肯定好唔想返中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369ecc2be29977d65e0d0a55ca3405278b4e4fe1","tid":2061752,"uid":55913,"like":101,"dislike":3,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"根本想投誠博攞居留<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed82ab1428c28feda3f72ae6474b78c0322be7cf","tid":2061752,"uid":352851,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"美帝亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc33e270bfff0468a6bc1c4984a3a42ab9f56447","tid":2061752,"uid":241399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.justice.gov/usao-ndca/pr/officer-china-s-people-s-liberation-army-arrested-los-angeles-international-airport\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-ndca%2Fpr%2Fofficer-china-s-people-s-liberation-army-arrested-los-angeles-international-airport&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=7e62344b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.justice.gov/usao-ndca/pr/officer-china-s-people-s-liberation-army-arrested-los-angeles-international-airport</a><br />\n<br />\nSAN FRANCISCO &ndash; Xin Wang, a scientific researcher and officer with the People&rsquo;s Republic of China&rsquo;s (PRC) People&rsquo;s Liberation Army (PLA), was arrested at Los Angeles International Airport (LAX) while attempting to depart the United States for Tianjin, China, and was charged with visa fraud, announced United States Attorney David L. Anderson and Federal Bureau of Investigation Special Agent in Charge John F. Bennett."},{"pid":"5e20b1fd3442766e263218d08d317daa2080d26a","tid":2061752,"uid":44243,"like":181,"dislike":0,"score":181,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"係呀 我解放軍黎架 你俾張綠卡我就咩都爆返出黎"},{"pid":"c95f94125ae6acf7c364c87772504628fde7ba8b","tid":2061752,"uid":8745,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好柒，中校做間諜都咁柒"},{"pid":"905e1a6567bc2e3225c11c21fc2bb05e6b101dfa","tid":2061752,"uid":296369,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:47:00.000Z","msg":"香港都有間碟學生，有國內學生出外國讀書是中共比錢的，當然要為國家做點事，將你學咗嘅或偷取嘅重要知識同資料上報返比中共，佢哋覺得呢啲係為國家服務但看在人哋眼裏就係一種間諜式嘅行為......<br />\n之前美國逐出嗰幾千個支那學生都係有中共軍方背景嘅，中國領事館喺網頁都叫佢哋小心清除晒佢哋自己電腦上嘅資料，以防美國海關官員會在機場檢查，其實都知佢哋係做間諜㗎啦，所以叫佢哋小心以免俾人捉到...."},{"pid":"9de9c4c784d5d9998b4e53d581b5dca6b47ac4ed","tid":2061752,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73c1af2a60847a89c603e3f3a41b02a17ccf3c9","tid":2061752,"uid":124711,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班老解要綠卡都唔要rmb"},{"pid":"c909a6f53541e12311fc765e41b7ffb60fbf826b","tid":2061752,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,